item.title: CVE-2021-24902|2024-08-03T19:49:13.867Z -- unknown -- typebot%20%7C%20build%20beautiful%20conversational%20forms
item.description: The Typebot | Build beautiful conversational forms WordPress plugin before 1.4.3 does not sanitise and escape the Publish ID setting, which could allow high privilege users to perform Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed.
